r />\n冇目標做乜都on99 人點你又點</blockquote><br />\n咁辛苦入咗做咩quit?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d0896b66ccd811d5b37a11615b889f18a40f40","tid":225403,"uid":13562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T18:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都讀唔成u<br />\n利申：asso仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連入場券都拎唔做，做死一世辛苦工</blockquote><br />\n入場券唔重要<br />\n最緊要揾到自己興趣同能力範圍<br />\n樓主介意講吓自己做緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做緊customer service 野，但我個人好奇怪，一長時間做同一樣野既時候就會覺得好悶，想轉環境，做黎做去都係一段時間就quit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要係根本搵唔到自己興趣"},{"pid":"0c157708191c08ca63a0383ccd305a0794556741","tid":225403,"uid":13562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T18:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same as you<br />\n<br />\n我留級 asso 再retake 入u 依家yr1又quit<br />\n冇目標做乜都on99 人點你又點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  exactly. <br />\n成日聽人講/睇到人地撈得好掂就想去試下，但做落又feel到依樣野其實唔岩自己"},{"pid":"884c9fd1ca11ac6e29c3267fcd0976b465b5c173","tid":225403,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Same as you<br />\n<br />\n我留級 asso 再retake 入u 依家yr1又quit<br />\n冇目標做乜都on99 人點你又點</blockquote><br />\n咁辛苦入咗做咩quit?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso係自己唔甘心<br />\n由細到大 老師屋企人社會老係話入u就掂<br />\n咪retake囉<br />\n入左U喇，個環境同讀既野未必真係岩自己<br />\n講真我對8大既科目冇一科有興趣<br />\n<br />\n醒覺太遲，跟住人行。<br />\n到依家比同屆同學遲咁多時候，又冇得點揀，好似要跟翻現實去行<br />\n<br />\n有時我都唔知自己做得岩定錯<br />\n點決擇？依家都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4344ed60111ca801b0a48fd6aefb3d700c357e0","tid":225403,"uid":13562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T18:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Same as you<br />\n<br />\n我留級 asso 再retake 入u 依家yr1又quit<br />\n冇目標做乜都on99 人點你又點</blockquote><br />\n咁辛苦入咗做咩quit?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso係自己唔甘心<br />\n由細到大 老師屋企人社會老係話入u就掂<br />\n咪retake囉<br />\n入左U喇，個環境同讀既野未必真係岩自己<br />\n講真我對8大既科目冇一科有興趣<br />\n<br />\n醒覺太遲，跟住人行。<br />\n到依家比同屆同學遲咁多時候，又冇得點揀，好似要跟翻現實去行<br />\n<br />\n有時我都唔知自己做得岩定錯<br />\n點決擇？依家都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n壓力大到日日訓都訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打其實依家發力都未算遲，我覺得依啲野係睇你有冇決心去做/去追近番同其他人既差距<br />\n<br />\n不過我有口話人冇口話自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccda45ebce1ddf3e9032dbbbff4556c558ed0bc5","tid":225403,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Same as you<br />\n<br />\n我留級 asso 再retake 入u 依家yr1又quit<br />\n冇目標做乜都on99 人點你又點</blockquote><br />\n咁辛苦入咗做咩quit?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso係自己唔甘心<br />\n由細到大 老師屋企人社會老係話入u就掂<br />\n咪retake囉<br />\n入左U喇，個環境同讀既野未必真係岩自己<br />\n講真我對8大既科目冇一科有興趣<br />\n<br />\n醒覺太遲，跟住人行。<br />\n到依家比同屆同學遲咁多時候，又冇得點揀，好似要跟翻現實去行<br />\n<br />\n有時我都唔知自己做得岩定錯<br />\n點決擇？依家都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n壓力大到日日訓都訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打其實依家發力都未算遲，我覺得依啲野係睇你有冇決心去做/去追近番同其他人既差距<br />\n<br />\n不過我有口話人冇口話自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家QuitU同出黎做野依2個選擇<br />\n揀左就定生死咁 搞到好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n互撐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得有興趣 就興趣行先 <br />\n有目標好好多<br />\n至少唔會後悔"}]}